Title: Designates state route 394 between the town of Kennedy and the village of Falconer, county of Chautauqua, as the "Staff Sergeant David Textor Memorial Highway"
Summary: Designates state route 394 between the town of Kennedy and the village of Falconer, county of Chautauqua, as the "Staff Sergeant David Textor Memorial Highway".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "Staff Sergeant David Textor Memorial Highway"
